{"tid":954671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【兒童馬拉松】小跑手起點仆低險釀人踩人 主辦單位致歉：賽事無安全審批","createTime":"2018-12-24T18:35:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T07:07:51.000Z","uid":130626,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a377d43281bd3708fbb8a3b8f122ea9873b04539","tid":954671,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T18:35:33.000Z","msg":"陝西西安昨日舉行兒童馬拉松，起跑時疑有人喊停，引發大混亂，中間位置有一名兒童摔倒在地，連帶身後幾名兒童也跌倒，情況十分混亂，差點造成造成人踩人慘劇。<br />\n西安雁塔區曲江城市運動公園舉辦兒童馬拉松。比賽開始僅1分鐘，就有多名小朋友不慎跌倒，身後的小跑手在不明的情況下，仍然試圖繼續往前擠擁，幸好有一名身份不明的男子在上台用擴音器宣佈比賽暫停，讓家長領回子女。小跑手隨後才停止前進，避免了一場踩踏事故。結果，逾千名家長衝破圍欄，跑到賽道上找已經開始跑步的子女，場面異常騷亂。據悉，拿擴音器喊暫停的男子已被警方帶走。<br />\n經了解，今次馬拉松活動有近1,000名5歲到9歲的兒童參加，賽事沒有通過安全審批。昨日深夜，賽事主辦單位發文道歉，承認審批手續不完備，將退回所有參賽費用。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xUzc6Gq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxUzc6Gq.png&h=5d1f01c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181224/59067315\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181224%2F59067315&d=OKDDIc6KTCI8N%2BpTXCU8oXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=bf53be68\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181224%2F59067315&h=0e182788\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181224/59067315</a>"},{"pid":"b018cdb1b64aa613c1b02b64a59aa53c5042ecc0","tid":954671,"uid":48582,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T18:47:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拿擴音器喊暫停的男子已被警方帶走。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98fc47cb8a2a7978884f444a0cc916dc822cd854","tid":954671,"uid":91096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b018cdb1b64aa613c1b02b64a59aa53c5042ecc0","tid":954671,"uid":48582,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyT